{"tid":2396012,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"[InSomnia]Dreamcatcher討論區(21) - 有DC的地方就是烏托邦","createTime":"2021-02-05T09:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T13:03:52.000Z","uid":1491,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d7303408d0d0586f19c9b5bed87aa1b78f686430","tid":2396012,"uid":1491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/474x/10/e1/44/10e144ae25c3d39ac016c058e5a0dd3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F474x%2F10%2Fe1%2F44%2F10e144ae25c3d39ac016c058e5a0dd3c.jpg&h=b81dcbaf&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\nDreamcatcher（韓語：드림캐쳐）是Happy Face娛樂在2017年推出的七人女子團體。其前身為2014年出道的五人女子團體MINX（韓語：밍스），成員包括祗攸、秀雅、始娟、裕賢、多美，於2017年以Dreamcatcher的名義重新出道並加入新成員韓東和佳泫。<br />\nDreamcatcher的粉絲名稱為「InSomnia」，意思為 在(In) 夢中(Somnia)，有著Dreamcatcher和飯們在夢中也能相見渡過幸福的時間，永遠一起的意思。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D-UWZIFUIAEaysr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD-UWZIFUIAEaysr.jpg&h=62efc994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDreamcatcher的官方應援色為🌕 PANTONE Black 6 C 🌘 PANTONE 7623 C 🌑 PANTONE P 10-6 C，意為 每當升起紅色月亮的日子，捕夢網會邀請大家一起做夢 (對應一周年Fan Song Full Moon結尾歌詞 像我永遠閃耀的夢一樣的心 充滿著紅色月光的滿月)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ErnKy_-VEAU_gkk?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FErnKy_-VEAU_gkk%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=272b0896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於出道四週年公布第一代<del>邪教會服</del>官方應援<del>勁長</del>手燈及披風<br />\n於2021年2月正式推出請期待<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4s2PjP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4s2PjP.png&h=1c72f514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3468m7o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3468m7o.png&h=366bf361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/185447_64c6d97b00c02daa7e098bef791a1573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F185447_64c6d97b00c02daa7e098bef791a1573.jpg&h=a86aaf4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DcR9W6jV4AIUg68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDcR9W6jV4AIUg68.jpg&h=7e9acd5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DnCujjWU4AE1EBO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDnCujjWU4AE1EBO.jpg&h=ed308c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DyyoqykVsAEnmqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDyyoqykVsAEnmqw.jpg&h=0e9ff154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EELAE_SUwAA01Wr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEELAE_SUwAA01Wr.jpg&h=d934331a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQe7Q9tVAAAHTjs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEQe7Q9tVAAAHTjs.jpg&h=bef5e465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EepQ7SDVAAMhewk?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEepQ7SDVAAMhewk%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=70d4b5e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ErwsMdOUwAEF4F5?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FErwsMdOUwAEF4F5%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=69b9e71c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">官方連結：</span><br />\n<br />\n專頁：<a href=\"http://www.dreamcatcher7.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dreamcatcher7.com&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=14613f83\" target=\"_b